import { HttpClient } from '@angular/common/http'; import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { Observable } from 'rxjs'; @Component({ selector: 'app-home', templateUrl: './home.component.html', styleUrls: ['./home.component.css'] }) export class HomeComponent implements OnInit { private apiUrl = 'http://localhost:8000/api/posts/last'; public sensorData: any; constructor(private http: HttpClient) { } ngOnInit(): void { this.getData().subscribe(data => { this.sensorData = data; }); } getData(): Observable { return this.http.get(this.apiUrl); } }
